The New Yorker offers a signature mix of reporting and commentary on politics, international affairs, and the arts, along with fiction, poetry, humor, and cartoons.

This pdf is "as it can be printed" for subscribers of the digital edition of The New Yorker, with full-page advertisements and the city-specific "Goings On About Town" sections left out.
